WEBVTT

00:00:12.313 --> 00:00:15.021
The final location is Golden Lake Plaza.

00:00:16.355 --> 00:00:18.938
One last step
and you'll make the headlines tomorrow.

00:00:27.563 --> 00:00:29.605
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:34.646
Fuck you, Wu Tien-chi.

00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:45.230
Yu-ching, Daddy's coming for you.

00:00:45.938 --> 00:00:46.855
Wang Cheng-nan!

00:00:49.021 --> 00:00:51.480
Stay away from me! Stay away.

00:00:51.563 --> 00:00:52.396
Okay.

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:54.896
-Stay away from me.
-Calm down.

00:00:55.438 --> 00:00:57.271
Don't do anything stupid. Come down.

00:00:57.355 --> 00:00:59.771
I'm sick of this corrupt world.

00:00:59.855 --> 00:01:02.146
The cops are useless fools too.

00:01:03.271 --> 00:01:05.480
I only need to jump.

00:01:05.563 --> 00:01:09.230
It'll go viral online and the police
will have to take her death seriously.

00:01:09.313 --> 00:01:12.063
Listen, we don't know
if it's Wang Yu-ching yet.

00:01:12.146 --> 00:01:14.855
We'll find the culprit soon.
There's still hope.

00:01:15.646 --> 00:01:17.896
-Come down.
-Stay away from me.

00:01:19.688 --> 00:01:20.563
I killed someone.

00:01:21.188 --> 00:01:23.146
I killed that bastard.

00:01:23.896 --> 00:01:28.146
-Chao, Wang Cheng-nan is going to jump.
-DNA confirms it wasn't Wang Yu-ching.

00:01:28.230 --> 00:01:31.188
We've got a new lead on his daughter.
Stop him now.

00:01:31.271 --> 00:01:33.188
Fuck you, Wu Tien-chi.

00:01:33.271 --> 00:01:36.355
That guy isn't dead. He's in hospital.
You didn't kill anyone.

00:01:36.438 --> 00:01:38.146
So don't do anything stupid.

00:01:38.230 --> 00:01:41.480
You're all lying to me.

00:01:42.313 --> 00:01:43.730
My daughter is dead.

00:01:44.230 --> 00:01:45.646
I killed someone.

00:01:45.730 --> 00:01:47.063
It's too late.

00:01:47.146 --> 00:01:48.438
-Too late.
-Wang Cheng-nan!

00:01:58.688 --> 00:02:00.438
I tried to kill myself once.

00:02:03.355 --> 00:02:04.938
I wanted it all to be over.

00:02:08.563 --> 00:02:09.855
But trust me.

00:02:12.605 --> 00:02:14.271
You'll regret it afterwards.

00:02:16.855 --> 00:02:17.938
I guarantee it.

00:02:22.146 --> 00:02:26.855
Think about your daughter.
What will happen to her if you die?

00:02:30.813 --> 00:02:32.230
-Yu-ching.
-Come down.

00:02:36.605 --> 00:02:38.855
Wait!

00:02:38.938 --> 00:02:41.063
She's alive! The DNA results are back.

00:02:41.146 --> 00:02:42.396
It's not your daughter.

00:02:43.396 --> 00:02:44.230
Don't jump.

00:02:48.813 --> 00:02:49.855
Hey!

00:03:17.021 --> 00:03:22.021
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:03:23.063 --> 00:03:27.063
THE DESCENT

00:03:50.855 --> 00:03:53.605
-Call an ambulance!
-Abductee found. Send an ambulance.

00:03:53.688 --> 00:03:56.355
-All units, abductee found.
-Get ready to clear a route.

00:03:56.438 --> 00:03:57.521
Wang Yu-ching.

00:03:58.396 --> 00:03:59.355
Wang Yu-ching!

00:04:12.605 --> 00:04:15.146
The guy you stabbed
wasn't fatally wounded.

00:04:15.230 --> 00:04:17.063
He's been moved out of ICU.

00:04:21.813 --> 00:04:23.521
Hey. Wipe your hands.

00:04:51.105 --> 00:04:52.230
Yu-ching.

00:05:01.021 --> 00:05:03.355
I'm here now.

00:05:24.980 --> 00:05:26.105
Wait a moment.

00:05:29.063 --> 00:05:30.688
Here. Take this.

00:05:34.188 --> 00:05:35.396
-Sister Lo.
-What?

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:37.438
You really won't leave?

00:05:38.230 --> 00:05:40.438
I want to stay here. You should go.

00:05:40.521 --> 00:05:44.605
Remember to eat properly. Got it?

00:05:53.146 --> 00:05:55.938
-Try not to miss me too much.
-I'm sure I'll get by.

00:06:34.980 --> 00:06:35.813
Sis.

00:06:42.771 --> 00:06:46.730
You've been hiding from me for so long.
You finally came to see me?

00:06:55.605 --> 00:06:57.230
I was staying away,

00:06:57.855 --> 00:07:01.021
in the hope you'd forget about me
and move on.

00:07:02.813 --> 00:07:04.480
I thought that with time,

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:06.896
you'd start to get over it.

00:07:07.813 --> 00:07:11.563
But it's been two years
and you still can't let me go.

00:07:14.896 --> 00:07:16.188
Stop being such a crybaby.

00:07:16.271 --> 00:07:19.480
And stop repeating my name
each morning like it's a sutra.

00:07:19.563 --> 00:07:20.730
It drives me nuts.

00:07:21.396 --> 00:07:24.480
Are you kidding? I'll never forget you.

00:07:25.980 --> 00:07:27.230
Idiot.

00:07:29.063 --> 00:07:30.980
I was never the smartest kid.

00:07:39.271 --> 00:07:44.313
Sis, I pray every day to the gods
to keep you safe and sound.

00:07:44.813 --> 00:07:48.563
How can I rest in peace
never knowing if you're safe?

00:07:50.188 --> 00:07:53.355
Do as Chieh says
and leave Dongfeng Market.

00:07:55.313 --> 00:07:56.771
I can't just leave you here.

00:07:56.855 --> 00:07:59.105
You're an earth-bound spirit.
You can't leave.

00:07:59.188 --> 00:08:01.521
It's not like we just
became ghosts yesterday.

00:08:01.605 --> 00:08:04.646
And the Third Crown Prince's
agent from above has our back.

00:08:04.730 --> 00:08:06.230
He won't let anyone hurt us.

00:08:08.271 --> 00:08:10.771
Will you come back and see me again?

00:08:13.313 --> 00:08:14.938
If you promise me one thing.

00:08:15.438 --> 00:08:16.271
What?

00:08:19.688 --> 00:08:21.563
Get used to life without me.

00:08:25.063 --> 00:08:27.355
And then get on with your life.

00:08:32.355 --> 00:08:34.188
Don't think about me too much. Just…

00:08:34.688 --> 00:08:35.980
Just every now and again.

00:08:41.646 --> 00:08:42.646
If…

00:08:43.688 --> 00:08:45.271
If fate permits it…

00:08:47.605 --> 00:08:49.396
we'll meet here again.

00:08:58.271 --> 00:08:59.105
Okay.

00:09:00.771 --> 00:09:02.230
I'll leave tomorrow.

00:09:25.521 --> 00:09:27.188
That was close.

00:09:29.021 --> 00:09:31.188
Yeah, good thing we pulled him back.

00:09:35.271 --> 00:09:36.480
Go ahead.

00:09:38.771 --> 00:09:39.605
Yes.

00:09:41.438 --> 00:09:42.271
Okay.

00:09:43.355 --> 00:09:44.396
Okay, got it.

00:09:45.355 --> 00:09:46.188
Fuck.

00:09:46.271 --> 00:09:47.980
Some guy who'd lost all his money

00:09:48.063 --> 00:09:50.938
jumped off a building
near the one Wang Cheng-nan was at.

00:09:51.563 --> 00:09:54.230
-What was the time of death?
-Around an hour ago.

00:09:55.146 --> 00:09:56.355
This is the deceased.

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:00.813
GENDER: MALE

00:10:02.938 --> 00:10:04.271
The elevator's broken.

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:06.563
Am I really doomed?

00:10:25.813 --> 00:10:27.813
-That bastard had a backup plan.
-Fuck.

00:10:27.896 --> 00:10:31.396
The magic array is complete.
He's channeling the Demon King's spirit.

00:11:53.813 --> 00:11:58.105
I finally made it up here.

00:12:08.730 --> 00:12:10.230
The full moon is tomorrow.

00:12:11.980 --> 00:12:13.605
The battlefield is Dongfeng Market.

00:12:15.896 --> 00:12:18.730
Fuck. Is this Stranger Things?

00:13:14.105 --> 00:13:15.146
Han Chieh.

00:13:16.938 --> 00:13:19.771
-Everyone's left. Why haven't you?
-The ghosts are still here.

00:13:19.855 --> 00:13:21.980
I got snacks for Hsiao-ming
and the grannies.

00:13:24.230 --> 00:13:26.563
I'm going to get some weapons from Fu.
Go home.

00:13:28.105 --> 00:13:30.063
Tonight's the showdown, isn't it?

00:13:33.313 --> 00:13:34.396
Yes.

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:37.021
Can I tag along today?
Just during the daytime.

00:13:40.521 --> 00:13:42.938
It's a free world. Do as you please.

00:13:43.021 --> 00:13:45.688
There's somewhere I want to go.
Can you come with me?

00:14:08.771 --> 00:14:09.896
After I got sick,

00:14:09.980 --> 00:14:14.313
I started coming here to clear my head
and wish upon this tree.

00:14:39.646 --> 00:14:42.980
It's become a ritual.
I always finish with a prayer.

00:14:50.438 --> 00:14:51.396
All done.

00:14:53.396 --> 00:14:56.230
-What did you wish for?
-World peace.

00:15:01.021 --> 00:15:03.980
-You really think this works?
-I do.

00:15:04.063 --> 00:15:05.438
The old guard told me

00:15:05.521 --> 00:15:07.771
that magic can't overcome divine power,

00:15:07.855 --> 00:15:11.105
divine power can't overcome karma
and karma can't overcome willpower.

00:15:11.605 --> 00:15:15.271
So someone with a wish
is even stronger than Doctor Strange.

00:15:15.896 --> 00:15:18.938
You really think a wish
can bring about world peace?

00:15:20.313 --> 00:15:21.438
You never know.

00:15:21.938 --> 00:15:25.188
My love for the world
is woven into that wish.

00:15:42.646 --> 00:15:43.646
If it makes you happy.

00:15:44.521 --> 00:15:45.813
Make a wish too.

00:15:50.605 --> 00:15:52.938
-I don't want to.
-Just one.

00:15:53.521 --> 00:15:55.855
Hey, just make one wish.

00:15:59.271 --> 00:16:03.396
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:17.521
Come on.

00:16:20.021 --> 00:16:21.771
We need to be ready.

00:16:25.938 --> 00:16:27.688
GOLDEN BRICK

00:16:58.396 --> 00:17:00.855
FUCK YOU AND DIE DEMON KING

00:17:01.605 --> 00:17:04.521
Han Chieh, will this really work?

00:17:05.396 --> 00:17:07.271
Works with ghosts, why not demons?

00:17:08.063 --> 00:17:10.271
Give me a hand. There's a lot to write.

00:17:17.563 --> 00:17:18.438
GO BACK TO HELL

00:17:38.146 --> 00:17:39.313
All done over there?

00:17:42.521 --> 00:17:43.688
DONGFENG RULES

00:17:43.771 --> 00:17:46.063
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S
AGENT FROM ABOVE WAS HERE

00:17:46.146 --> 00:17:47.521
INVINCIBLE THIRD CROWN PRINCE

00:17:47.605 --> 00:17:49.063
DONGFENG RULES

00:17:49.146 --> 00:17:51.188
CHIEH KICKS ASS

00:17:54.396 --> 00:17:56.938
FUCK OFF BACK TO HELL

00:18:21.230 --> 00:18:23.771
Fuck. Eight won't be enough.

00:18:27.646 --> 00:18:28.730
Han Chieh.

00:18:33.021 --> 00:18:35.313
It's almost time. You should go home.

00:18:35.396 --> 00:18:37.230
Is there anything else I can do?

00:18:39.813 --> 00:18:42.605
You can go home and take your meds.
That's all I ask of you.

00:18:43.188 --> 00:18:44.188
Han Chieh.

00:18:45.355 --> 00:18:47.063
You think the wishing tree is dumb.

00:18:47.896 --> 00:18:49.855
Make a wish to the Third Crown Prince.

00:18:55.521 --> 00:18:57.521
Wish for victory tonight.

00:18:58.105 --> 00:18:59.021
Okay?

00:19:03.438 --> 00:19:05.105
Whether he helps or not,

00:19:06.188 --> 00:19:07.563
I'm not going to beg.

00:19:10.563 --> 00:19:11.605
Also,

00:19:13.438 --> 00:19:15.313
having hope

00:19:16.855 --> 00:19:18.688
only hurts more after it's gone.

00:19:39.313 --> 00:19:42.563
Old guard, what are you doing?
Why haven't you left yet?

00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:50.146
This is my home. Why should I leave?

00:19:50.646 --> 00:19:52.813
-Why are you staying?
-Why are you staying?

00:19:52.896 --> 00:19:54.688
The agent from above has to stay.

00:19:54.771 --> 00:19:58.396
Perfect. I'm applying to be
Lord Guan's agent from above.

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:02.438
Have you met him?
He doesn't want you. Just drop it.

00:20:02.521 --> 00:20:04.938
If the old guard's staying,
I'm not going either.

00:20:05.021 --> 00:20:06.396
Stay out of this.

00:20:07.521 --> 00:20:10.813
You have to go. Fighting is for men.

00:20:15.771 --> 00:20:17.188
Fried chicken.

00:20:17.855 --> 00:20:18.980
Spareribs.

00:20:20.105 --> 00:20:22.730
Spring rolls. Fried chicken.

00:20:27.146 --> 00:20:30.813
-I told you to wait at home, why--
-Spring rolls… Fried chicken.

00:20:32.188 --> 00:20:33.146
Spareribs.

00:20:34.563 --> 00:20:35.730
Spring rolls.

00:20:36.521 --> 00:20:37.396
Fried chicken.

00:20:39.813 --> 00:20:40.646
Fried chicken.

00:20:40.730 --> 00:20:41.563
Spare--

00:20:46.313 --> 00:20:48.605
I was getting takeout.
What am I doing here?

00:21:18.688 --> 00:21:19.605
Chieh?

00:21:21.063 --> 00:21:23.230
-Why am I back here?
-What's going on?

00:21:23.938 --> 00:21:25.688
They grew a conscience and came back?

00:21:26.271 --> 00:21:28.438
No, they've been possessed.

00:21:30.146 --> 00:21:31.646
Must be Wu Tien-chi's doing.

00:21:32.896 --> 00:21:34.396
What's the bastard up to?

00:21:35.730 --> 00:21:38.063
Should everyone leave or go home?

00:21:40.563 --> 00:21:41.730
It's getting dark.

00:22:12.605 --> 00:22:14.938
Come up, all of you.

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:25.688
Go to Dongfeng Market.

00:22:25.771 --> 00:22:28.938
Say hello to Han Chieh for me.

00:22:29.563 --> 00:22:30.938
This time,

00:22:31.563 --> 00:22:34.146
no one can stop me

00:22:34.230 --> 00:22:38.355
from getting my demonic power back.

00:23:03.355 --> 00:23:04.646
DONGFENG RESIDENTS ONLY

00:23:04.730 --> 00:23:05.688
Watch the steps.

00:23:07.980 --> 00:23:09.521
-Have some water.
-Here.

00:23:18.688 --> 00:23:19.521
Chieh.

00:23:20.771 --> 00:23:23.771
What's going on out there?
Are they coming?

00:23:26.188 --> 00:23:29.605
They should be here soon.
He's waiting for the moon to rise.

00:23:31.021 --> 00:23:34.438
Old guard, this will last all night.
Can you make it through?

00:23:34.521 --> 00:23:39.480
Hey, I've got your back.
I'll hold on as long as it takes.

00:23:41.146 --> 00:23:44.480
-Got a kitchen knife?
-What for? Killing ghosts?

00:23:44.980 --> 00:23:45.855
Yes.

00:23:46.813 --> 00:23:48.646
I only have a few milk caps left.

00:23:48.730 --> 00:23:51.688
I have to save them for the Demon King.

00:23:52.521 --> 00:23:57.146
Get the talismans I gave you before.
Putting them on weapons will help.

00:23:58.855 --> 00:24:01.396
Leafy, Sister Lo, Mei-na.

00:24:03.480 --> 00:24:05.730
Get everyone's keys.

00:24:05.813 --> 00:24:08.396
Get any supplies that we can use.

00:24:08.480 --> 00:24:10.605
Prepare for battle!

00:24:41.146 --> 00:24:44.063
We're going into battle.
What's with the idols and blankets?

00:24:44.146 --> 00:24:45.980
Han Chieh!

00:24:47.021 --> 00:24:48.355
Something's gotten in.

00:27:15.563 --> 00:27:17.563
-What gun is that?
-The gun of kindness.

00:27:17.646 --> 00:27:21.271
Kindness, my ass. Our guns and bullets
have been blessed by Lord Guan.

00:27:21.355 --> 00:27:23.605
Fu taught us.
Why aren't you using your milk caps?

00:27:23.688 --> 00:27:24.771
I wish I could.

00:27:58.771 --> 00:28:00.063
Get lost.

00:28:13.438 --> 00:28:14.813
Why are they leaving?

00:28:14.896 --> 00:28:16.521
-They're gone.
-What's going on?

00:28:16.605 --> 00:28:18.938
Ms. Wang. Open the door.

00:28:19.521 --> 00:28:20.771
Open the door.

00:30:01.271 --> 00:30:03.938
Wu Tien-chi's coming.
Get in there and protect them.

00:30:04.021 --> 00:30:06.730
-Good thing Fu taught us this.
-And Chieh opened my third eye.

00:30:06.813 --> 00:30:10.730
Chieh, my heart's about to give out.
This is freaking terrifying.

00:30:17.771 --> 00:30:18.605
Where's Leafy?

00:30:19.313 --> 00:30:20.313
Where is she?

00:30:25.063 --> 00:30:26.188
Protect them.

00:30:31.230 --> 00:30:32.438
Have you seen Leafy?

00:30:32.938 --> 00:30:34.313
Isn't she with you?

00:30:40.146 --> 00:30:41.563
First floor.

00:30:47.688 --> 00:30:48.938
Let's get inside.

00:31:17.063 --> 00:31:17.980
Wu Tien-chi.

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:19.563
Not so fast.

00:31:36.980 --> 00:31:39.438
You think those female ghosts
appeared in her home

00:31:39.521 --> 00:31:42.313
because her mom went to see
some lame feng shui master?

00:31:47.771 --> 00:31:49.355
Hi, Master Han. I'm Leafy.

00:31:49.438 --> 00:31:51.771
Someone put this under my dad's pillow.

00:31:51.855 --> 00:31:53.438
A female ghost enchanted him.

00:31:57.771 --> 00:32:00.188
She has always been

00:32:00.938 --> 00:32:03.480
a pawn the Demon King placed beside you.

00:32:05.521 --> 00:32:07.438
I sent those ghosts
to her home every night

00:32:09.855 --> 00:32:11.396
to blow demonic energy

00:32:12.396 --> 00:32:13.688
into her body.

00:32:14.896 --> 00:32:17.521
And refine her liver
into my demonic liver.

00:32:25.938 --> 00:32:28.313
It's been a while, little punk.

00:32:46.063 --> 00:32:49.313
You've matured since our last encounter.

00:32:51.980 --> 00:32:55.063
My punches hit harder now too.
Wanna find out for yourself?

00:32:59.730 --> 00:33:05.146
Compared to the other agents
I've fought in the past,

00:33:05.230 --> 00:33:09.230
the feel of your fist on my face
is so much more…

00:33:09.980 --> 00:33:11.313
satisfying.

00:33:11.396 --> 00:33:13.313
Cut the bullshit.

00:33:13.396 --> 00:33:17.105
You sucked Chen Chi-sha dry
and used Leafy to refine a liver

00:33:17.188 --> 00:33:18.730
to cultivate a new assistant,

00:33:19.438 --> 00:33:20.563
Wu Tien-chi, right?

00:33:20.646 --> 00:33:21.980
Wu Tien-chi?

00:33:23.980 --> 00:33:26.896
He's evil enough,
but doesn't have the talent.

00:33:26.980 --> 00:33:30.438
Surely a demonic liver
would be wasted on someone like him.

00:33:37.521 --> 00:33:39.646
I want you to have it.

00:33:41.313 --> 00:33:42.146
Me?

00:33:42.230 --> 00:33:45.480
You're younger than Chen Chi-sha
and stronger than Wu Tien-chi.

00:33:45.563 --> 00:33:47.146
Why not you?

00:33:50.688 --> 00:33:52.730
I'm so jealous of the Third Crown Prince.

00:33:52.813 --> 00:33:55.688
How did he find such a great assistant?

00:33:56.938 --> 00:33:58.146
Come work for me.

00:33:58.813 --> 00:34:01.563
I'll treat you better
than the Third Crown Prince does.

00:34:01.646 --> 00:34:04.021
You can have anything you want.

00:34:04.105 --> 00:34:07.063
You can kill whoever you want.

00:34:11.646 --> 00:34:13.438
I prefer messing with scum like you.

00:34:14.271 --> 00:34:16.313
Like I prefer scraping shit off my shoe.

00:34:16.896 --> 00:34:20.021
So you only fight bad guys, right?

00:34:22.105 --> 00:34:23.271
Hang on.

00:34:24.521 --> 00:34:26.980
You got your whole family killed.

00:34:28.813 --> 00:34:31.188
You're just as much of a bad guy.

00:34:33.105 --> 00:34:35.980
That's why I'm
fucking slaving away for him.

00:34:38.521 --> 00:34:43.980
You know,
if you accept this demonic liver,

00:34:44.063 --> 00:34:46.896
you will gain immense demonic power,

00:34:47.605 --> 00:34:50.938
and finally be rid
of the Third Crown Prince.

00:34:52.105 --> 00:34:54.521
You can become my agent

00:34:54.605 --> 00:34:57.521
and conquer all three realms with me.

00:34:57.605 --> 00:34:59.188
Fuck you. I'm not interested.

00:35:02.438 --> 00:35:04.688
Do you think you have a choice?

00:35:06.105 --> 00:35:09.938
It's too late.
The demonic liver has fully grown.

00:35:10.021 --> 00:35:13.771
It could burst out of her body
at any moment and rip her to pieces.

00:35:18.521 --> 00:35:20.771
Do you want her
to suffer such a tragic death?

00:35:32.188 --> 00:35:35.230
I'll trade livers,
but only on two conditions.

00:35:36.438 --> 00:35:38.521
Spare all the humans and ghosts here.

00:35:39.813 --> 00:35:40.688
And two.

00:35:44.355 --> 00:35:45.271
Give her my liver.

00:35:48.313 --> 00:35:49.438
She must live.

00:35:54.105 --> 00:35:57.146
But she's already doomed to die.
Didn't you know?

00:35:59.355 --> 00:36:00.563
What do you mean?

00:36:01.480 --> 00:36:04.355
Her leukemia has spread.

00:36:05.521 --> 00:36:07.063
All this time,

00:36:07.146 --> 00:36:11.105
only the power of the demonic liver
has been keeping her alive.

00:36:15.146 --> 00:36:16.063
She didn't tell you?

00:36:21.021 --> 00:36:22.188
After I got sick,

00:36:22.271 --> 00:36:24.980
I started coming here to clear my head.

00:36:25.063 --> 00:36:27.771
You really think a wish
can bring about world peace?

00:36:28.730 --> 00:36:29.771
You never know.

00:36:29.855 --> 00:36:31.521
Han Chieh, smile.

00:36:32.771 --> 00:36:35.938
My love for the world
is woven into that wish.

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:43.063
Every extra day is worth it.

00:36:47.146 --> 00:36:49.438
Okay, I'll do it.

00:36:53.896 --> 00:36:55.730
But you must give her my liver.

00:36:56.730 --> 00:36:58.813
I have to know she's still alive

00:36:59.771 --> 00:37:01.563
before I accept your demonic liver.

00:37:06.271 --> 00:37:08.521
I've killed so many people,

00:37:09.813 --> 00:37:11.855
but this is my first time saving one.

00:37:15.313 --> 00:37:17.063
Once you're working for me,

00:37:17.146 --> 00:37:19.480
don't ever talk to me like that again.